room_title: Escape room "Bloody Elbow" by Quest Room in Los Angeles
room_address: 170 South Western Avenue, Los Angeles, CA 90004
room_description:
It is the 14th century and everyone is ruled by Holy Inquisition. You have been accused of witchcraft and have been incarcerated to await your awful death by the hands of “Bloody Elbow”. He is a famous executioner known for his love of painful tortures and bloody deaths…
You have only one hour to try your test fate and escape the dreadful dungeon in the guarded castle before he returns to finish what he started!
